Jesus loves you all so much He died on the cross for you in your place! Since we deserve eternal death because we are human and we sin, we automatically fall short of Godâ€™s glory. God understood this, and became human in the form of Jesus. Jesus taught us not to hate, but to love everyone. He is God, and washed the feet of others to teach us to care for one another. Not to judge. 

So, what is sin? Sin is going against Godâ€™s will. After we sin once, we should be dead and separated from God. BUT. JESUS DIED FOR US ON THE CROSS. He picked up His cross and carried it and only thought of you. He felt pain, loneliness, sadness, anxiety, happiness, love, joy, and temptation. God became human and experienced everything humans experience. He understands you. 

Think youâ€™re too unclean or sinful for Him? Think about this: do you go to a bath already clean? No, you go to a bath to get clean. When you sin, go to God first. He is bigger than any of our sins combined. He made the universe and heaven! He cares for you. 

Things get tough and sometimes you may question if God is even there. But He is. Think of this: when you first ride your bike without training wheels, you will fall and scrape your knees. Itâ€™s not easy, but you learn, and become better and better as you practice! God puts us through lessons! He is there every step of the way, so we donâ€™t need to be afraid of anything! He builds us. Once you give your surrender to Him, let Him guide you. 

How can you surrender to God? Tell God right now â€œGod, I believe what Jesus did for me. I want to start new with You. I accept You into my life. Forgive me Lord, You are my salvation.â€ (It doesnâ€™t need to be word for word, just be genuine, and He can help you with being genuine as well). Sometimes, you wonâ€™t know what to do or say. And thatâ€™s okay, youâ€™re not perfect. But God is!! Trust in His forgiveness. You are made right with God through faith in Him and what He can do. A lot can happen in a week. Jesus has been through it. One day, everyone was shouting â€œHosanna: Blessed is the King of Israel that cometh in the name of the Lord.â€ (John 12:13) A few days later, those same people praising Him were yelling â€œCrucify Him!â€ But, He rose from the dead! He conquered death, and now sits at the right Hand of God the Father Almighty. You are made new in the Holy Spirit Who is also the same One God, in Spirit form. The Father, the Son, and the Holy Spirit are One God combined. They are all equally God. The Holy Spirit will remind you of Godâ€™s word. Godâ€™s voice is often thought of as loud, scary, or thunderous. No, Godâ€™s voice is quiet, gentle, and knows exactly what to say in your mind. He can also speak through other people and things, but it must relate back to His word . If it doesnâ€™t, itâ€™s not from God. If it rushes you, makes you anxious, or pressures you, itâ€™s not God, itâ€™s the enemy trying to impersonate God. But donâ€™t worry! God is with you on your side ready to be your shield always. He is power is bigger than anything, and any evil. You can read Godâ€™s word on Bible.com! His presence is lovely, and relaxing. He wants a relationship with you now!
â€œNow this is eternal life: that they know You the true God and Jesus Christ, whom You have sent.â€ (John 17:3). Itâ€™s not about if youâ€™re  just a good person. Itâ€™s about knowing God and having faith in Him. When you have faith in God, He will guide your works to glorify Him and to help you to become the best version of you. Start new with God today. Youâ€™re ready to. Spread this message! â¤

author: @kuju2315
text:
Stray kids is a legendary group with the most diverse discography. Stray kids are huge in the music industry. They are top producers . Only groups in k-pop that are  self made ( chan picked the members) and self produced groups .
From the newest  album 5 star,Rock Star and lose my breath,hall of frame ,FNF, item,leave ,cover me, the sound, super bowl, Youtiful,blind spot,time out and obviously S-Class, lalalala etc . 

Soft song - never ending, winter fall,4419, spread my wings, 24 to 25, OH, leventer, blue print, Ex, red light, hoodie season,for you , lonely st, silent cry,charmer, on track,time out, novel , there, the view your eyes,  blue print, star lost etc. 

Brilliant song - venom, freeze, grrr, mirror, miroh, maze of memories, chronosaurus, 3racha  side effect ,top, 3racha , slump,god's menu, thunderous, TA, cheese,muddy water, the sound, slump,top etc.

Old gems - hellevator, district 9, my pace, awkward silence,19, road not taken,boxer, question,M.I.A,get cool,I am you , yayaya, grow up , stop, booster, astronaut, maze of memories,side effects, mixtape 1,2,3,4, entrance, hero's soup,my side etc.
From start to now they give so many beautiful songs.

People need to watch the intro of each album to know how they come up with the idea and concept and meaning behind the song and all details and work they do on every song.

Stray kids are known for the quality of music and dedication for music.They are very creative and unique and versatile.  Stray kids is inspiring to so many people. Their music is something connected with  people .They give motivation, inspiration  to express yourself it's ok to be unique You are beautiful the way you are. stray kids discography is very diverse with life philosophy. 
I describe stray kids music is
"EXPRESSION OF LIFE"
EXPRESSION OF PEOPLE" "EXPRESSION OF EMOTIONS"
 Lyrics are beautifully expressed with  so many meanings . 
They have a diverse discography. I love the  intellect, cleverness and creativity in songs. They have a very organic,fresh and  unique sound. They didn't limited themself and explore the new side of music. You see so many new, refreshing and experimental sounds in their music. text:
Stray kids They are definitely  dominating  the k-pop. They are huge in  the music industry. They are top producers. They are the  most successful group we have . 
Stray kids have all quality which make them legends of k-pop . Plus also make apart  from other generation of group like Big Bang, exo, Bts, snsd, black pink, twice and other many groups is -
 
â€¢  Self- made - They are the First fully self made group in k-pop. Chan picked all group members,  they made the name,concept, and logo.
 On the other hand other groups are made by the company.

â€¢ Self- produce - Stray kids is a self produced group from the start of their discography made by themselves. They are the ones to make  beats, melody, write lyrics, compose songs,record the song,and edit, arrange the song etc. other groups become successful thanks to other producers, composers, and lyricists. 

â€¢  Innovation - They step out  from stereotypes of music and make new organic , fresh creative,innovative music that is lacking  in other groups, other groups play safe to please the people and make repetitive songs. 

â€¢ Artistic value -stray kid's half of group is doing dance , producing, composing, writing songs before they debut ( 3racha and Lee know backup dancer) and with skz player and skz record they always give music to the world because they love what they do. On the other hand see Many other idols are coming to industry for stardom,frame and money they didn't care about music and doing other things like modeling, acting,advertising etc forgetting about their main job singing and creating music.

"EXPRESSION OF PEOPLE'S"

â€¢  Genius Lyricists - they are  very  clever,creative and unique, with many Wordplay, 3-4 different meanings in lyrics. That is very rare in the k-pop industry. Hellevator, noeasy, oddinary, chronosaurus, Rock is the example of this.

author: @irisheyes9912
text: I absolutely love this song & a few words stuck out, like "lungs"  and "lose my breath" .  I'm really sick & found out I have pneumonia in both lungs and the Dr said the X-rays show a neoplasm nodule in my lung (I don't remember which one).  I have to get more X-rays done in 3-4 weeks to get a clearer image once the pneumonia starts to clear up.  From there they will biopsy it & go from there.  I love singing, & the thought of not singing again is so depressing.  I've had cancer before, it runs in my family on both sides, my dad has it again for the 2nd time.  I'm sorry, I'm just still in shock, I just found out about my diagnosis earlier today.

author: @liza_pet
text: Seungmin's vocals and visual are just something unthinkable and incomprehensible. I can't take my eyes off him from the first second of the first day, but now I don't even have words to describe how much he has changed and grown, and in all meaningful ways. Seungmini is not only divinely beautiful, he literally shines brighter than the stars, eclipsing absolutely everything and everything. And his unique voice conquered my heart irrevocably and definitively from the first note, but with what power and strength it sounds now, what professional level has it reached. If I thought so before, now I am absolutely sure that Seungmin is not just ready, but will shine even brighter with his solo album.

author: @liza_pet
text:
Seungmin always puts so many feelings 
and emotions into absolutely every song, in absolutely every part and note. A voice that just needs to be heard as tears flow like a stream and my heart is pounding so fast jumping out of my chest and I can't do anything about it at all. He was perfectly in control of his voice from the very beginning and how much he has grown during this time, what a high professional level he has reached and nevertheless continues to improve and continues to work. Seungmin is the real treasure not only of STRAY KIDS, not only of the K-POP industry, but of the entire music world. In so many years in the K-POP industry, I have never met such an idol as Seungmin, in fact, I shouldn't have because he really is the only one.

author: @liza_pet
text:
I've always had and will have a little of Seungmin, I can't stop being amazed by him in this song, video and album as a whole. He has changed 
so much, matured and grew up at a professional level, although very little time has passed since the S-CLASS comeback and it is impossible to recognize Seungmin. Even his look has become completely different, more confident, and his eyes sparkle even brighter, as well as the visual of Seungmini is unrealistically beautiful, but what he is now cannot be described in any words, that's honestly I can't. He perfectly owns his voice amazing high notes angelic timbre and it has always been so only now his vocals have truly opened up with new power and force thundering all over the world. I just love the way he dances, his style of movement is so natural, while absolutely always clear and clean, it's really given to him, and with this choreography he blew up and burned everything around such a colossal return. I'm looking forward to Seungmin's solo album more than anything.

author: @liza_pet
text:
Seungmin's voice is an ocean of tears, a 
heart that jumps out of his chest and a soul 
torn apart, not every vocalist is capable of this. His voice is clear as crystal, soft as a cloud deeper than the ocean and at the same time 
as strong as a hurricane.

author: @liza_pet
text:
No record, no disc will transfer all the beauty, depth, strength and power of Seungmin's voice. The most precious diamonds and the brightest stars are hidden from human eyes, and it's not for nothing that when I met Seungmin, 
I understand this like never before.

author: @liza_pet
text:
Literally every album every song and every performance of Seungmin's voice is a discovery, it never ceases to amaze, and to such an extent that you lose not only the power of speech but also your pulse. A voice that I want to listen to endlessly and how much more potential there 
is in it, I'm even afraid to imagine. I will never 
stop admiring Seungmin and praying for his 
solo album.

The voice is clear as crystal, soft as a cloud, and the timbre is so sweet, solid honey, but at the same time so sensual and deep that it immediately 
penetrates into your heart. I PRAY TO 
ALL THE GODS FOR HIS SOLO ALBUM.

text: As soon as you hear Seungmin's voice, your heart jumps out of your chest like tears and your soul is torn apart, and not every vocalist is capable of this. His voice is clear as crystal, soft as a cloud and deeper than the ocean, while being as strong and powerful as a hurricane. Seungmini is the real diamond not only of STRAY KIDS but of the entire K-POP industry.
